    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062520/extras/7d436caaed534bec7e7bed4761dba2a1.avif?t=1769944417\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062520/extras_big/7d436caaed534bec7e7bed4761dba2a1.avif?t=1769944417 width=800 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>警告：本视频游戏可能引发光敏性癫痫发作。建议玩家自行酌情定夺。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><u>重要提示： 本游戏围绕探索展开，缓慢营造紧张氛围，打造更加深刻、有意思的体验。故事情节随着离奇的画面、周围环境微小的细节层层推进。请记住，本游戏为难度较高的非传统游戏。</u></i><strong></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062520/extras/3984e9f80fde7ed6a4e6462bf2b43793.avif?t=1769944417\" width=616 height=96 /></span><strong><br>Nightmare Within</strong> – 一款由独立创作者使用虚幻引擎 5 开发的恐怖氛围游戏。用手电筒探索房子的黑暗角落，在努力不尖叫的同时解决谜题。  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>叙事：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主角半夜醒来，感觉家里有入侵者。他无法理解前方会发生什么。想起自己以低价购买了这栋位于偏远地区的房子，疑虑开始困扰他。主人公患有一些精神问题，导致出现幻觉。他最初以为这只是他的焦虑，但当他伸手去拿药时，他意识到有人在跟踪他。他决定离开房子，结束幻觉，但有东西或有人阻止了他，将他困在自己的家中，陷入幻觉之中。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特点：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你的声音就是你的敌人</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中包含一些令人恐惧的时刻，可能会吓到你并引起它的注意。尽量不要发出声音或低声说话，否则它会找到你。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062520/extras/354de080410ca9539d7201436841f30b.poster.avif?t=1769944417\" width=616 height=215 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062520/extras/354de080410ca9539d7201436841f30b.webm?t=1769944417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>恐怖氛围</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏让你沉浸在孤独的房子和主角噩梦的氛围中。物体会改变位置，门会自己吱吱作响，灯光会闪烁着奇怪的颜色。雷声和雨声的怪异声音会让你一直处于紧张之中。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062520/extras/592c8460887c8a757887bb1ac75dfd74.poster.avif?t=1769944417\" width=616 height=215 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062520/extras/592c8460887c8a757887bb1ac75dfd74.webm?t=1769944417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏玩法</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索每个房间以了解正在发生的事情，低声对自己说，以免引起可能隐藏在阴影中的任何东西的注意。解决谜题，监控手电筒的电池寿命，并收集逃离房屋所需的物品。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062520/extras/b56bdf30a3daa4a5bbc1cdfdd49120c7.poster.avif?t=1769944417\" width=616 height=215 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3062520/extras/b56bdf30a3daa4a5bbc1cdfdd49120c7.webm?t=1769944417\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
